FLUPS DEPENDENCIES
-----------------------------------------


This program is distributed with external contributions from other libraries which are or not under the same license.

External dependencies distributed with this program:
- si.hpp    2-clause BSD    https://github.com/GalSim-developers/GalSim)


This program has also external dependencies on other libraries and website depedencies which are or not undet the same license and that re commonly used with this program core librarries.

External dependencies for this program:
- h3lpr     3-clause BSD    https://github.com/vanreeslab/h3lpr 
- HDF5      3-clause BSD    https://www.hdfgroup.org


Finally this program has external dependencies to API which can be fullfilled by any library complient to the requirements and which are or not under the same license.

External API dependencies for this program.
- fftw3.h   https://www.fftw.org/
- MPI 3.1   https://www.mpi-forum.org/mpi-31/


